  "instructions": [
    "Heat the manteca in a large skillet over medium heat.",
    "Add the chopped onion and cook until softened, about 5 minutes.",
    "Add the minced garlic and cook for 1 minute, until fragrant.",
    "Add the diced tomato and bell pepper, and cook for 5 minutes, until tender.",
    "Add the falafel patties, chopped cilantro, and lime juice to the skillet, and stir to combine.",
    "Continue cooking for 5-7 minutes, until the falafel is heated through and the sauce has thickened.",
    "Season with salt to taste, and serve immediately on a salt block, garnished with fresh cilantro."
